Independent Pulse public-client wire peer for sing-openconnect M4.

The IF-T/TLS, EAP, and EAP-TTLS wire behavior is independently implemented
from pulse.c in OpenConnect commit
2035601b64a5360a46d18e08937e7f654b3230f2. It reuses no production parser or
cryptographic implementation; the peer side of TLS uses the system Python
OpenSSL-backed ssl module.
